Bingo Caller
------------

This app is Catalyst based (perl) and is designed to be a web based simple bingo machine, that would be used at a bingo evening.

Objective:

Set a game up (location, max_number_drawn value, assume lowest value will be 1, number_of_seconds before next number can be drawn)

Click to 'draw' a random number from the range 1 -> max_number_drawn.

Display that.

After number_of_seconds, allow to click to draw another, unique random number.

Button to press if someone calls bingo, which will bring up grid of previously called numbers, highlighting last number called.

Allow to restart game if bingo was not correct, else freeze game, and allow new game to be started.

Show previous 10 numbers drawn at the bottom of the screen, as game is progressing.